headline: How Recent Developments Are Reshaping the lululemon Investment Story
summary: Analysts have recently revised their consensus price target for lululemon athletica, decreasing it slightly from $198.36 to $195.84. This adjustment reflects a more cautious tone across much of Wall Street as sentiment around the company's growth and execution capabilities becomes increasingly mixed.
